## 🛠 SCRIPTS

### Feature Generator — Always the first step for a new feature
```bash
dart run scripts/feature_generator.dart {feature_name}
```
Examples:
```bash
dart run scripts/feature_generator.dart products
dart run scripts/feature_generator.dart order_items
```

Generates the folder structure with a `@freezed` State and a ready Cubit.

> ⚠️ **The script generates placeholder files that MUST be cleaned up immediately after running:**

| File generated by script | REST | GraphQL |
|---|---|---|
| `data/models/{name}_model.dart` | ❌ **Rewrite** — remove `@freezed`, use `fromJson` + `toEntity()` | ❌ **Rewrite** — remove `@freezed`, use `fromGql(GqlType)` + `toEntity()` |
| `data/models/{name}_model.freezed.dart` | ❌ **Delete** | ❌ **Delete** |
| `data/models/{name}_model.g.dart` | ❌ **Delete** | ❌ **Delete** |
| `domain/usecases/{name}_usecases.dart` | ❌ **Delete** — uses old patterns; write your own usecase file instead | ❌ **Delete** |
| `domain/params/{name}_params.dart` | ❌ **Delete** if usecase takes no params (use `NoParams`) / **Rewrite** if params needed | ❌ **Delete** if no params / **Rewrite** extending `UseCaseParams` if params needed |
| `presentation/{name}_screen.dart` | ❌ **Delete** if no Figma link was provided — NEVER generate UI without Figma | ❌ **Delete** if no Figma link was provided |
| `presentation/widgets/{name}_body.dart` | ❌ **Delete** if no Figma link was provided | ❌ **Delete** if no Figma link was provided |

> 🔑 **GraphQL data model rule:** For GraphQL features, the model file **exists** but uses a different pattern:
> - Use `fromGql(GqlType gql)` factory instead of `fromJson`
> - Add `toEntity()` to map to the domain entity
> - The repository calls: `Model.fromGql(parsedItem).toEntity()` — clean and consistent
> - **No raw `fromJson` needed** — the generated `.graphql.dart` type already handles JSON parsing

> ✅ **Keep:** `domain/repositories/`, `data/datasources/`, `data/repositories/`, `presentation/cubits/` — rewrite their content.
> ✅ **Keep:** `domain/entities/` folder — create your own entity files inside it.

**Other available scripts:**
```bash
dart run scripts/asset_class_generator.dart   # Regenerate Assets class
dart run scripts/language_generator.dart      # Regenerate locale classes
dart run scripts/font_family_generator.dart   # Regenerate font families
dart run scripts/add_app_icon.dart            # Generate app icons
dart run scripts/asset_yaml_generator.dart    # Auto-link assets in pubspec.yaml
dart run scripts/font_yaml_generator.dart     # Auto-link fonts in pubspec.yaml
dart run scripts/generate_flavors.dart        # Generate build flavors interactively
```

