## 🌍 TRANSLATIONS (ALWAYS REQUIRED)

### When to add translations
Add translation keys for any user-visible text: screen titles, field labels, error messages, empty state messages.

### Step 1 — Add to both files

**`assets/translations/en.json`:**
```json
{
  "featureTitle": "Feature Title",
  "featureEmptyMsg": "No items found",
  "featureErrorMsg": "Failed to load items"
}
```

**`assets/translations/ar.json`:**
```json
{
  "featureTitle": "عنوان الميزة",
  "featureEmptyMsg": "لا توجد عناصر",
  "featureErrorMsg": "فشل تحميل العناصر"
}
```

### Step 2 — Regenerate locale_keys.g.dart
```bash
flutter pub run easy_localization:generate -f keys -O lib/resources -S assets/translations -o locale_keys.g.dart
```

### Step 3 — Use in code
```dart
import 'package:flutter_base_template/resources/locale_keys.g.dart';
import 'package:easy_localization/easy_localization.dart';

Text(LocaleKeys.featureTitle.tr())
```

✅ Never hardcode strings in the UI — always use `LocaleKeys.xxx.tr()`

