## 🎭 SHIMMER — For Loading States

### Difference between `ShimmerLoadingWidget` and `SkeletonWidget`

| Widget | Usage |
|---|---|
| `ShimmerLoadingWidget(child:...)` | **Wrapper** — applies shimmer animation to white Containers inside it |
| `SkeletonWidget(width:, height:)` | **Standalone** — a single shimmer rectangle element |

> ⚠️ **Important rule:** Do NOT put `SkeletonWidget` inside `ShimmerLoadingWidget` — each has its own shimmer. Use only one at a time.

### Correct shimmer pattern for lists

```dart
// ✅ Correct approach
Widget _buildShimmerList() {
  return Container(
    margin: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 16),
    clipBehavior: Clip.antiAlias,          // ← required for borderRadius clipping
    decoration: BoxDecoration(
      color: Colors.white,
      borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(16),
    ),
    child: ShimmerLoadingWidget(
      baseColor: const Color(0xFFE0E0E0),       // ← always set explicitly
      highlightColor: const Color(0xFFF5F5F5),  // ← otherwise shimmer may be invisible
      child: ListView.builder(
        padding: EdgeInsets.zero,
        itemCount: 10,
        shrinkWrap: true,                        // ← required to avoid layout errors
        physics: const NeverScrollableScrollPhysics(),
        itemBuilder: (_, index) => Column(
          mainAxisSize: MainAxisSize.min,
          children: [
            _buildShimmerItem(),
            const DashedDivider(color: Color(0x33919EAB)),
          ],
        ),
      ),
    ),
  );
}

Widget _buildShimmerItem() {
  return Padding(
    padding: const EdgeInsets.all(16),
    child: Row(
      children: [
        // ✅ White Container — responds to ShimmerLoadingWidget parent
        Container(
          width: 40, height: 40,
          decoration: BoxDecoration(
            color: Colors.white,
            borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(500),
          ),
        ),
        const SizedBox(width: 16),
        Expanded(
          child: Column(
            crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,
            mainAxisSize: MainAxisSize.min,
            children: [
              Container(
                width: 120, height: 14,
                decoration: BoxDecoration(
                  color: Colors.white,
                  borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(4),
                ),
              ),
              const SizedBox(height: 6),
              Container(
                width: 180, height: 12,
                decoration: BoxDecoration(
                  color: Colors.white,
                  borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(4),
                ),
              ),
            ],
          ),
        ),
      ],
    ),
  );
}
```

### When to use `SkeletonWidget` standalone
```dart
// ✅ Correct — SkeletonWidget used independently
SkeletonWidget(width: 120, height: 14)

// ❌ Wrong — SkeletonWidget inside ShimmerLoadingWidget (double shimmer = broken)
ShimmerLoadingWidget(child: SkeletonWidget(...))
```

