### `AvatarWidget` — Usage example
```dart
AvatarWidget(
  imageUrl: user.profileImage,
  initial: user.firstName?.getFirstAndLast ?? user.email.getFirstAndLast,
  radius: 20,
  backgroundColor: const Color(0xFFDFE3E8),  // fallback: scheme.primaryContainer
