### `RefreshCubit` — For rebuilding UI in Forms
```dart
// Available at: lib/shared/blocs/refresh/refresh_cubit.dart
// Used in login screen to force rebuild when form field values change
final _refreshCubit = RefreshCubit();

BlocBuilder<RefreshCubit, RefreshState>(
  bloc: _refreshCubit,
  builder: (context, _) { ... },
)

// Force a rebuild:
_refreshCubit.refresh();
```

