## 🏗 Feature Structure (Clean Architecture)

```
lib/Features/{feature}/
  ├── data/
  │   ├── models/           ← Data models: fromJson/toJson (no freezed for models)
  │   ├── datasources/      ← Remote datasource (+ Local for auth/caching)
  │   └── repositories/     ← Repository impl (extends BaseRepository)
  ├── domain/
  │   ├── entities/         ← Pure Dart (no fromJson/toJson)
  │   ├── enums/            ← Feature-specific enums (only if needed)
  │   ├── params/           ← Only if usecase needs params; use NoParams otherwise
  │   ├── repositories/     ← Abstract repository interface
  │   └── usecases/         ← Use cases (business logic)
  └── presentation/
      ├── cubits/           ← Cubit (@freezed state) + state file
      ├── widgets/          ← Widgets used only within this feature
      └── pages/            ← Screen widgets (@RoutePage)
```

### Architecture Rules
| Layer | Rule |
|---|---|
| DataSource | Uses feature `*ApiService` (Retrofit, not Dio directly), returns `ApiResponse<T>`, no try-catch |
| Repository Impl | extends `BaseRepository`, uses `handle()`, maps models → entities, no manual try-catch |
| Domain Entities | Pure Dart, no fromJson, no imports from data layer |
| Use Case | `@injectable`, wraps a single repository call |
| Cubit | Depends on Use Case (not repository directly) |
| State | `@freezed` mandatory |

