## 🔍 Pre-Generation Checks

### CHECK 1: Existing Models
```
lib/core/foundation/contracts/   ← ApiResponse, PaginationDataEntity, PaginationQuery
lib/core/foundation/errors/      ← Failure sealed types
lib/Features/*/domain/entities/
lib/Features/*/data/models/
```
→ Reuse if a matching entity already exists.

### CHECK 2: Existing UI Components
Before building any widget, check `lib/shared/widgets/` and extensions.
✅ Reuse what exists instead of creating new.

### CHECK 3: Domain Layer
Every new feature must have: entities + repositories + usecases.

