### `PaginationBuilderWdg` Parameters
```dart
PaginationBuilderWdg<CubitType, EntityType>(
  contentPadding: EdgeInsets.zero,       // overrides default 24px horizontal padding
  loadingItemsWidget: shimmerWidget,     // shown before any data is fetched (loading / initial)
  loadingItemWidget: loadingIndicator,   // shown while loading additional pages (success + isLoading)
  itemWdg: (item) => ItemWidget(item),   // widget per list item
  allItemWdg: (items) => CustomList(),   // full list replacement (optional)
  separatorWidget: const DashedDivider(),
  notItemsMsg: 'No items found',         // text for EmptyStateWidget
  emptyList: const CustomEmptyWidget(),  // replace EmptyStateWidget (optional)
  wantKeepAlive: false,                  // keep state alive in PageView
)
```

