## 🚫 UI Generation Rules

> **NEVER generate a screen or UI widgets unless a Figma link is explicitly provided.**
>
> - No Figma → generate API flow only (data + domain + bloc)
> - With Figma → generate screen + widgets after completing the API flow
> - If the feature_generator created `{name}_screen.dart` or `widgets/{name}_body.dart` and no Figma was provided → **delete them immediately**

