## 📋 Generation Order

### REST:
1. Run `dart run scripts/feature_generator.dart {feature}` (new feature)
2. `domain/entities/{entity}.dart`
3. `domain/entities/{name}_page.dart` (if paginated)
4. `domain/repositories/{feature}_repository.dart`
5. `domain/usecases/{use_case}.dart`
6. `data/models/{model}_model.dart` (+ request model if POST/PUT)
7. `data/models/{name}_response.dart` (if paginated)
8. `data/datasources/{feature}_api_service.dart` (Retrofit — per feature)
9. `data/datasources/{feature}_remote_datasource.dart`
10. `data/repositories/{feature}_repository_impl.dart`
11. `presentation/cubits/{name}_cubit.dart` (with `part freezed` + `part state`)
12. `presentation/cubits/{name}_state.dart` (non-paginated only)
13. Update `lib/core/infra/network/rest/api_urls.dart`
14. `presentation/pages/{name}_screen.dart` (if Figma provided)
15. Update `lib/routes/router.dart` (if Figma provided)
16. Update translations `assets/translations/ar.json` + `en.json`
17. `dart run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs`
18. `flutter pub run easy_localization:generate -f keys -O lib/resources -S assets/translations -o locale_keys.g.dart`

### GraphQL:
> ⚠️ **build_runner runs TWICE for GraphQL:**
> - **Run 1** — after writing the `.graphql` document → generates the `.graphql.dart` typed classes
> - **Run 2** — after writing all feature files → generates `freezed` + updates `injection.config.dart`

1. Run `dart run scripts/feature_generator.dart {feature}` (new feature)
   - Then **immediately delete** `data/models/{name}_model.dart` — rewrite it with `fromGql` + `toEntity` pattern
2. **If operation NOT yet generated:**
   - Create `lib/core/network/gql/config/documents/{mutations|queries}/{name}.graphql` with the definition
   - **Run 1:** `dart run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs`
   - Verify file generated: `.../{mutations|queries}/generated/{name}.graphql.dart`
3. Confirm generated file path and read the class names (`Options$`, `Variables$`, `Mutation$`/`Query$`, nested types)
4. `domain/entities/{entity}.dart` (one file per nested GQL type)
5. `domain/params/{name}_params.dart` (if needed — extends `UseCaseParams`)
6. `domain/repositories/{feature}_repository.dart`
7. `domain/usecases/{use_case}.dart`
8. `data/models/{name}_model.dart` — `fromGql(GeneratedType)` + `toEntity()` for each nested type
9. `data/datasources/{feature}_remote_datasource.dart` (uses `GQLService.mutate/query`)
10. `data/repositories/{feature}_repository_impl.dart` (imports `gql_service.dart` for `QueryResultExt`)
11. `presentation/cubits/{name}_cubit.dart`
12. `presentation/cubits/{name}_state.dart`
13. `presentation/pages/{name}_screen.dart` (if Figma provided)
14. Update `lib/routes/router.dart` (if Figma provided)
15. Update translations `assets/translations/ar.json` + `en.json`
16. **Run 2:** `dart run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs`
17. `flutter pub run easy_localization:generate -f keys -O lib/resources -S assets/translations -o locale_keys.g.dart`

> 🔧 **If feature classes are missing from `injection.config.dart` after build_runner:**
> ```bash
> dart run build_runner clean
> dart run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs
> ```
> This happens when a previous build had errors that got cached. Clean + rebuild fixes it.

