## ✅ Final Checklist

### General (REST + GraphQL)
- [ ] Package name: `flutter_base_template` in all imports
- [ ] State uses `@freezed` with `part '...freezed.dart'` in the Cubit file
- [ ] Cubit depends on UseCase (not Repository)
- [ ] Paginated Cubits extend `PaginationCubit<E>` (no state file) + **`close()` override calls `_useCase.cancel()`**
- [ ] Shimmer: `ShimmerLoadingWidget` (white Containers inside) + explicit colors
- [ ] Separators: `DashedDivider` from `shared/widgets/`
- [ ] Translations: added to ar.json + en.json + locale_keys.g.dart regenerated
- [ ] UI text: `LocaleKeys.xxx.tr()` only — no hardcoded strings
- [ ] Params class (if usecase needs input): extends `UseCaseParams` + `const {Name}Params(...) : super()`
- [ ] DI: Repository registered as abstract type
- [ ] build_runner: executed after generation
- [ ] Screen: `@RoutePage()` + route added in `router.dart`
- [ ] Shared widgets: any reusable widget goes in `lib/shared/widgets/` and exported from `widgets.dart`

### REST only
- [ ] URL added in `core/infra/network/rest/api_urls.dart`
- [ ] Feature ApiService: `Features/{feature}/data/datasources/{feature}_api_service.dart` (Retrofit)
- [ ] Failure: `core/foundation/errors/failure.dart` (use `BusinessFailure` — no `ErrorModel`)
- [ ] ApiResponse: `core/foundation/contracts/api_response.dart`
- [ ] Repository extends `BaseRepository`, uses `handle()` — no manual try/catch
- [ ] Cancel: `DioCancelTokenWrapper` from `core/infra/network/cancellation/`, `resetCancelToken(false)` in UseCase

### GraphQL only
- [ ] `data/models/{name}_model.dart` uses `fromGql(GqlType)` factory (not `fromJson`) + `toEntity()` method
- [ ] Every nested GQL type has its own Model class with `fromGql` + `toEntity()`
- [ ] Repository parses response with generated `fromJson`: `Mutation$Op.fromJson(res.data as Map<String, dynamic>)` → `Model.fromGql(...).toEntity()`
- [ ] **Never** access `res.data!['key']['field']` directly — always use the generated typed class
- [ ] build_runner ran **twice**: once for `.graphql.dart` generation, once for `freezed` + `injection.config.dart`
- [ ] Feature classes appear in `injection.config.dart` — if missing, run `build_runner clean` then rebuild
- [ ] Generated file identified: `lib/core/network/gql/config/documents/{mutations|queries}/generated/`
- [ ] DataSource uses `GQLService.mutate()` or `GQLService.query()` with `CancelInstance`
- [ ] Repository imports `gql_service.dart` for `QueryResultExt` (`res.success`, `res.errorMessage`) — **mandatory, without it you get "getter not defined" compile errors**
- [ ] Params class (if any) extends `UseCaseParams` with `const {Name}Params(...) : super()`
- [ ] Repository error handling: `on GraphQLError` (not `DioException`)
- [ ] UseCase extends `BaseUseCase` and reads `languageCode` from context via `getIt<AppRouter>()` (only when the GQL operation needs it)
- [ ] Cancel: `CancelInstance`, `resetCancelToken(true)` in UseCase
- [ ] GQLService depends on `AuthLocalDatasource` (NOT `AuthRepository`) — no circular deps
- [ ] `GQLService._initializeClient()` is called in the constructor (client must be ready at first use)
- [ ] After login success: call `getIt<GQLService>().setToken(token)` or `initWithIso()` in the UseCase so GQL picks up the auth token
